  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They thought, either I am a drunk which doesn't know what he's talking about, or I'm a provocateur talking about the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You want to know what the people say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they moved out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately, next stop, another idiot came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 187,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I got to play around again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I played till I came to the state I got to go up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had been a drunkard, what can I do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[MUMBLING] [HICCUP] [MUMBLING] [HICCUP] That Hitler is a swine, and is very, very bad to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans are killing us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody wake up to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[HICCUP] And everybody walked out of the tram.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I went further a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Again, people came up, and then again, down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 188,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Till I went to my wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 189,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 190,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 191,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people didn't want to take me in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 192,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took me in eventually because--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 193,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people which Luba was there with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 194,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they said that I am burned from the ghetto, and someone will see me will recognize.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 195,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we convinced her, and she let us stay a few days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 195,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved to another place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 196,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we prepared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 196,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did have a lot of Christian--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 197,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Contacts, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we'd been during the time of the Christian side, we'd been going from one place to another one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did that for a few bad things too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went, once, to a place, for example, where I went to a party of 20 people which was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when the birthday [NON-ENGLISH] of the holy [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 198,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH] sits at his place, the [NON-ENGLISH], which is now called [NON-ENGLISH], got the birthday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 199,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but the-- if you-- Oh Jesus Christ.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
